name: Among the Stars
description:
I sometimes aspire to achieve something big that I am often blinded by the opportunities that have been there all along. Many times I don’t accomplish something because of the big ambitions that are out of reach.

Maybe I will never reach the moon, maybe I won’t get the bigger prize but being thankful for the accomplishments I achieve no matter how small is the true meaning of life. Celebrating every moment makes every journey in life more meaningful. Taking small steps each day so I can look back and see how far I have come. Maybe one day, a seemingly impossible dream will soon become a reality.
